    <title type="html"><![CDATA[郵局信箱（專用信箱）收到掛號信件的電子郵件 E-Mail 通知]]></title>
    <link href="http://life.sars.tw/blog/2016/03/30/you-ju-xin-xiang-(zhuan-yong-xin-xiang-)shou-dao-gua-hao-xin-jian-de-dian-zi-you-jian-e-mail-tong-zhi/"/>
